  "title": "APAC Systems Applications Engineer (AV/ Pro Audio)/ MNC/$7.5k basic+VB/Central",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Up to basic $7,500 + Bonus + Benefit.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Permanent role/ 5 workdays/ Marymount area</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Lead end-to-end AV / audio system design, deployment, and optimization across APAC preferred.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Global leading provider of innovative security and professional communication solutions.</strong></p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide pre-sales and technical support to sales and business development teams.</p></li><li><p>Lead end-to-end AV / audio system design, deployment, and optimization across APAC.</p></li><li><p>Support product launches, NPIs, and technical demonstrations.</p></li><li><p>Deliver technical training and certification for distributors and system integrators.</p></li><li><p>Support partners on technical performance and solution development.</p></li><li><p>Assist in pipeline and opportunity development.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Key Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma/ Degree in IT, Audio-Visual, or related field.</p></li><li><p>5 years’ experience in Pro Audio / AV systems.</p></li><li><p>Strong system design and BOM capability (EASE, AutoCAD, SketchUp).</p></li><li><p>Experience working with consultants, integrators, and channel partners.</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills; regional travel required [Open for discussion]</p></li><li><p>Industry certifications (AVIXA, Dante, EASE, CCNA) preferred.</p></li></ul><p><strong>How to apply</strong><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the position, you may send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">search84@searchindex.com.sg</a><br /><strong>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly.</strong><br /><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong><br /><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
